OL,3,CDavina McCall reveals she is
OL,4,Cundergoing surgery for 'rare' brain
OL,5,Ctumour
OL,7,FThe TV presenter says she is in 'good
OL,8,Fspirits' after being diagnosed with a
OL,9,Fbrain tumour, as ITV News reporter
OL,10,FFaye Barker has more
OL,12,FDavina McCall has revealed she is
OL,13,Fundergoing surgery for a "very rare"
OL,14,Fbrain tumour.
OL,16,FIn an Instagram video on Friday, the
OL,17,FTV presenter asked her fans to "say a
OL,18,Fprayer" for her as she prepared for
OL,19,Fsurgery to remove the benign tumour,
OL,20,Fknown as a colloid cyst.
