OL,3,CDavina McCall reveals she is
OL,4,Cundergoing surgery for 'rare' brain
OL,5,Ctumour
OL,7,FAddressing her followers, she said: "A
OL,8,Ffew months ago I did a menopause talk
OL,9,Ffor a company and they offered me a
OL,10,Fhealth scan in return which I thought
OL,11,FI was going to ace. It turns out I had
OL,12,Fa benign brain tumour called a colloid
OL,13,Fcyst which is very rare, three in a
OL,14,Fmillion."
OL,16,F"I slightly put my head in the sand
OL,17,Ffor a while, then I saw quite a few
OL,18,Fneurosurgeons and I realised that I
OL,19,Fhave to get it taken out," she added.
