OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe 'My Mum, Your Dad' host said she
OL,13,Fwould be having a craniotomy to remove
OL,14,Fthe 14-millimetre-wide tumour.
OL,16,FJoined in the video by her partner
OL,17,FMichael Douglas, the 57-year-old said:
OL,18,F"Say a prayer for me. I'm in good
OL,19,Fspirits."
