OL,5,Ctumour
OL,7,FShe continued: "I'm okay, it's been up
OL,8,Fand down obviously. We've been through
OL,9,Fa lot."
OL,11,FMcCall said her recovery in hospital
OL,12,Fwould last nine days and she will be
OL,13,Foff her phone while she recovers at
OL,14,Fhome.
OL,16,FShe said: "I don't want you to worry
OL,17,Fabout me, I'm doing enough as it is.
OL,18,FI'll see you on the other side."
